OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foccasionally heavy and thundery rain
OL,7,Fthis evening, clearing away southeast
OL,8,Fthrough the early hours. The rest of
OL,9,Fthe night remains cloudy but largely
OL,10,Fdry. Freshening southeasterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA rather cloudy start but
OL,13,Fsunny spells developing through the
OL,14,Fmorning. Staying dry in the afternoon
OL,15,Fwith some sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
