OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fmorning Saturday with occasional rain
OL,7,Fbut afternoon brighter. Rain spreading
OL,8,Feast overnight then clearing early
OL,9,FSunday, then the rest of Sunday and
OL,10,FMonday breezy with sunny spells and
OL,11,Fshowers.
